WEBVTT

00:00:00.373 --> 00:00:02.389
Track 12.05

00:00:04.233 --> 00:00:05.233
Narrator: 1

00:00:06.083 --> 00:00:08.187
A: What are you going to do this morning?

00:00:09.088 --> 00:00:13.820
B: I’m going to clean the house – and you’re going to help me!

00:00:15.244 --> 00:00:16.300
Narrator: 2

00:00:17.397 --> 00:00:21.208
A: So, is he going to play the piano this evening?

00:00:21.632 --> 00:00:24.101
B: Yes, he is.

00:00:24.881 --> 00:00:26.596
Are you going to listen?

00:00:28.020 --> 00:00:29.202
Narrator: 3

00:00:30.451 --> 00:00:34.032
A: What are you and your friends going to do in the holidays?

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:35.566
B: I don’t know.

00:00:35.591 --> 00:00:38.115
We’re going to talk about it this afternoon.

00:00:39.285 --> 00:00:40.182
Narrator: 4

00:00:41.167 --> 00:00:43.358
A: Where’s she going to watch TV?

00:00:44.147 --> 00:00:45.885
B: In the living room.

00:00:47.088 --> 00:00:48.239
Narrator: 5

00:00:48.810 --> 00:00:52.532
When am I going to do all these things on my list?